snippet.title: BBQGuys
snippet.description: Were you Born to Grill™? Of course you were; why else would you be reading the “About” section of our YouTube channel? While you’re here, we might as well clue you in on what you can expect: grilling recipes from a diverse and talented team of culinary creators, Grillabilities® that give you the skills to grill, expert overviews to help you shop smarter, and whatever else we can cook up for your sizzling satisfaction. Who knows, there might even be more Manning commercials heading to a notification near you! That’s enough reading for today — it’s time to subscribe, sit back, and enjoy the show.
